I don&#39;t know the psychtoolbox, but assuming that you can get an underlying numeric matrix that corresponds to tex, in MATLAB, you can mirror/reflect any matrix using:

    newMatrixHorizontallyReflected = fliplr(oldMatrix);

or

    newMatrixVerticallyReflected = flipud(oldMatrix);

I&#39;ll assume you can either modify the data that underlies the existing texture or create a new texture with reflected data.

